OL,3,CPolice force destroys records relating
OL,4,Cto Miners' Strike and Orgreave
OL,6,FA police force has destroyed records
OL,7,Frelating to the Miners' Strike and the
OL,8,F'Battle of Orgreave' ahead of an
OL,9,Finquiry into the violence.
OL,11,FNorthumbria Police has confirmed it
OL,12,Fdisposed of two boxes containing data
OL,13,Frelating to the year-long strike, more
OL,14,Fthan 40 years ago, in April last year.
