OL,3,CPolice force destroys records relating
OL,4,Cto Miners' Strike and Orgreave
OL,6,FAnd in the House of Commons on
OL,7,FThursday, Labour's Ian Lavery, MP for
OL,8,FBlyth & Ashington, called for an
OL,9,Furgent debate as he described the
OL,10,Fdestruction as "absolutely alarming".
OL,12,F"Is this the systematic attempt to
OL,13,Fobscure justice? I'm not sure if
OL,14,Fanyone is prepared to ask that
OL,15,Fquestion," he said, later adding:
OL,16,F"Justice cannot be served if the
OL,17,Fevidence is systematically and
OL,18,Fdeliberately destroyed."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
