OL,6,FIn response, Lucy Powell MP, Leader of
OL,7,Fthe House of Commons, said she would
OL,8,Fcontinue to raise the issues with
OL,9,Fgovernment ministers.
OL,11,FShe told MPs: "I would join him in
OL,12,Fsaying to people anyone involved that
OL,13,Fthey must retain the records and they
OL,14,Fmust come forward, as they would be
OL,15,Fexpected to do when those questions
OL,16,Fare asked, with every bit of
OL,17,Finformation they have got on what
OL,18,Fhappened."
