OL,6,FMeanwhile a group campaigning for an
OL,7,Finquiry into the 'Battle of Orgreave'
OL,8,Fhas labelled the force's move as
OL,9,F"extremely disturbing".
OL,11,FKate Flannery, secretary of the
OL,12,FOrgreave Truth and Justice Campaign,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We are now understandably
OL,14,Fworried about how many other police
OL,15,Fforces may have recently destroyed or
OL,16,Fintend to destroy important
OL,17,Finformation that would be very
OL,18,Frelevant in an Orgreave inquiry or
OL,19,Finvestigation."
