OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FYvette Cooper, who is now the Home
OL,12,FSecretary, wrote to police forces
OL,13,Finvolved in the policing at Orgreave
OL,14,Fin December 2016 in her role as Chair
OL,15,Fof the Home Affairs Committee.
OL,17,FShe asked them to tell the committee
OL,18,Fwhat information they had on Orgreave
OL,19,Fthat was not already in the public
OL,20,Fdomain.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
