OL,6,FThe chief constable of Northumbria
OL,7,FPolice at the time, Steve Ashman,
OL,8,Fresponded later in December 2016.
OL,10,FHe said they had found 15 documents
OL,11,Frelating to the clashes at Orgreave on
OL,12,F18 June 1984, detailed what two of the
OL,13,Fdocuments related to, and said they
OL,14,Fwere available to the committee if
OL,15,Frequested.
