OL,6,FKevin Horne, miner arrested at
OL,7,FOrgreave on 18 June 1984, said: "Any
OL,8,Fargument that documents and records
OL,9,Fwere simply destroyed on the basis of
OL,10,Ftime passed does not make sense given
OL,11,Fthat Northumbria police and other
OL,12,Fpolice forces had by April 2024,
OL,13,Falready kept the documents for nearly
OL,14,F40 years."
